<F P=100> RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russian Embassy Employee Killed in Algiers </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2803183494 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 
1800 GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2803183494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Konstantin Kukukshin, an employee of the Russian 
Embassy, was killed today in the southern outskirts of the 
Algerian capital. This was reported by the country's security 
services. He is the fourth Russian representative killed in 
Algeria in the past six months. 

</TEXT>

