<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Georgian Residents Refuse To Leave </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2903165094 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1445 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2903165094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Abkhazian Svaneti, 29th [dateline as received] -- 
The IBERIA news agency has learned that the majority of the 
Kodori Gorge Georgian population refuses to leave and are ready 
to protect their households with arms in hands. 

</TEXT>

