<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Supreme Council Confirms New Finance Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2903193894 Tbilisi First Program Television Network in 
Georgian 1800 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2903193894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi First Program Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Today, the Georgian Supreme Council confirmed Davit 
Iakobidze as finance minister. The issue of merging the 
Ministries of Finance and Economy was raised at the session. 
Should the Supreme Council confirm it, the finance minister 
will be in charge of the united ministry. 
  As it is important and urgent to confirm the Cabinet of 
Ministers, the Supreme Council decided to convene on 30 March at 
1200 [0800 GMT]. 

</TEXT>

