<H3> <TI>   Russian Commander Issues Order on Defense Against Attacks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3003201294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1830 GMT 
30 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3003201294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Commander of the Russian 14th Army in the Dniester 
region, Lieutenant General Aleksandr Lebed, has issued an order 
to the units in his command to be firm to the point of using 
arms in stopping any attempted attacks on installations and 
servicemen. As the commander's press secretary reported, the 
decision was made in connection with previous instances of 
attacks on Russian soldiers and threats from armed mafia groups 
to harm them and members of their families. This information 
was received through ITAR-TASS channels. 

</TEXT>

